title: el-Mahasna
description: Predynastic cemetery site approximately 8 miles north of Abydos. A small settlement was built on the site in the Early Dynastic period.

properties.description: Point representing the location of the Predynastic cemetery and Early Dynastic settlement at al-Maḥāsna, derived from an OpenStreetMap Node after AofE.
